. * --- 3a. feTR ---
. di _n "--- feTR decomposition ---"

--- feTR decomposition ---

. cap noisily twowayfeweights Dl_hpi county year Linter_bra, type(feTR) weight(
> w1) summary_measures

Under the common trends assumption,
the TWFE coefficient beta, equal to 0.0103, estimates a weighted sum of 6473 AT
> Ts. 
4406 ATTs receive a positive weight, and 2067 receive a negative weight.
------------------------------------------------
Treat. var: Linter_bra  # ATTs      Σ weights  
------------------------------------------------
Positive weights        4406        1.1244      
Negative weights        2067        -0.1244     
------------------------------------------------
Total                   6473        1.0000      
------------------------------------------------

Summary Measures:
TWFE coefficient (β_fe) =    0.0103
min σ(Δ) compatible with β_fe and Δ_TR = 0:    0.0085
min σ(Δ) compatible with treatment effect of opposite sign than β_fe in all (g,
> t) cells:    0.0296
Reference: Corollary 1, de Chaisemartin, C and D'Haultfoeuille, X (2020a)


The development of this package was funded by the European Union (ERC, REALLYCR
> EDIBLE,GA N°101043899).

. if _rc == 0 {
.     local fetr_ok = 1
.     * Capture results
.     local fetr_beta    = e(beta)
.     local fetr_npos    = e(num_pos_w)
.     local fetr_nneg    = e(num_neg_w)
.     local fetr_ntot    = `fetr_npos' + `fetr_nneg'
.     if `fetr_ntot' > 0 {
.         local fetr_pneg = 100 * `fetr_nneg' / `fetr_ntot'
.     }
.     else {
.         local fetr_pneg = 0
.     }
.     cap local fetr_sumn = e(sum_neg_w)
.     if _rc != 0 local fetr_sumn = .
. 
.     di _n "--- feTR Summary ---"

--- feTR Summary ---
.     di "  beta       = " %9.4f `fetr_beta'
  beta       =    0.0103
.     di "  Pos weights: " `fetr_npos'
  Pos weights: .
.     di "  Neg weights: " `fetr_nneg'
  Neg weights: .
.     di "  % Negative:  " %5.1f `fetr_pneg' "%"
  % Negative:      .%
.     if `fetr_sumn' != . di "  Sum neg w:   " %9.4f `fetr_sumn'
. }

. else {
.     di "feTR FAILED with rc=" _rc
.     local fetr_ok = 0
. }

. 
. * --- 3b. fdTR ---
. di _n "--- fdTR decomposition ---"

--- fdTR decomposition ---

. cap noisily twowayfeweights Dl_hpi county year Linter_bra, type(fdTR) weight(
> w1) summary_measures
invalid syntax

. if _rc == 0 {
.     local fdtr_ok = 1
.     local fdtr_beta    = e(beta)
.     local fdtr_npos    = e(num_pos_w)
.     local fdtr_nneg    = e(num_neg_w)
.     local fdtr_ntot    = `fdtr_npos' + `fdtr_nneg'
.     if `fdtr_ntot' > 0 {
.         local fdtr_pneg = 100 * `fdtr_nneg' / `fdtr_ntot'
.     }
.     else {
.         local fdtr_pneg = 0
.     }
.     cap local fdtr_sumn = e(sum_neg_w)
.     if _rc != 0 local fdtr_sumn = .
. 
.     di _n "--- fdTR Summary ---"
.     di "  beta       = " %9.4f `fdtr_beta'
.     di "  Pos weights: " `fdtr_npos'
.     di "  Neg weights: " `fdtr_nneg'
.     di "  % Negative:  " %5.1f `fdtr_pneg' "%"
.     if `fdtr_sumn' != . di "  Sum neg w:   " %9.4f `fdtr_sumn'
. }

. else {
.     di "fdTR FAILED with rc=" _rc
fdTR FAILED with rc=198
.     local fdtr_ok = 0
. }

